00:19:19,890 --> 00:19:21,020
What are you saying?

320
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:21,720
Senior.

321
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:23,300
Someone's coming.

322
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:39,280
Master Cheng.

323
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:44,210
Yique Yinyang's accomplice?

324
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,830
Where is the criminal, Tang Lici?

325
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:48,070
He fell into the Celestial River

326
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,240
and disappeared without a trace.

327
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:51,490
The water of Celestial River
is freezing cold,

328
00:19:51,490 --> 00:19:53,210
making it impossible to search underwater.

329
00:19:53,210 --> 00:19:54,400
If you can't find

330
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:55,750
who you're looking for here,

331
00:19:55,750 --> 00:19:56,790
you might as well go down the mountain

332
00:19:56,790 --> 00:19:57,880
and search along the river.

333
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:58,940
If that's the case,

334
00:19:59,030 --> 00:20:01,350
why are you still lingering here,
Island Master?

335
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:03,550
I'm here to visit the Chief
of Biluo Palace.

336
00:20:03,550 --> 00:20:04,160
Then why are those two

337
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:05,620
also standing guard here?

338
00:20:07,860 --> 00:20:08,460
Everyone.

339
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:10,880
The Yique Yinyang, Tang Lici,

340
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:11,740
have vanished.

341
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:12,790
Why don't we

342
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:13,930
stay where we are

343
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:15,020
