00:21:52,510 --> 00:21:54,520
The Sword Alliance and Fengliu Shop

384
00:21:54,540 --> 00:21:57,000
have encountered each other
at the entrance of Biluo Palace.

385
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:57,310
I'm afraid

386
00:21:57,310 --> 00:21:59,240
your days of staying out of jianghu

387
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:00,850
are coming to an end.

